## 11. Test Failures to Expect

### Button Tests
1. **`aria-disabled` not found**: PF6 uses `disabled` attribute instead of `aria-disabled` when `isDisabled` is set (except when `component` is not "button"). `aria-disabled` only renders when `true`.
   - **Fix**: Remove tests checking for `aria-disabled="false"` or checking `aria-disabled` matches `isDisabled`

2. **`byText` returns wrong element**: A wrapping `div` around button text means RTL `byText` returns the wrapper, not the button.
   - **Fix**: Use `byRole('button', { name: 'text' })` instead of `byText('text')`

### Select Tests
1. **`byRole` can't find menu options**: After selection, Popper menu may be set to `aria-disabled`, causing RTL to not find items.
   - **Fix**: Pass `{ hidden: true }` option to query, or set `appendTo="inline"`

### General Test Impacts
- Any snapshot tests will break due to class prefix changes (`pf-v5-` тЖТ `pf-v6-`)
- Any tests checking specific CSS variables will break
- Any tests checking for specific OUIA component types with `PF5/` prefix will need `PF6/` prefix
- Markup structure changes in many components will break shallow render snapshots

---

## 12. Manual Steps After Codemods

### Must-Do Checklist

- [ ] **Update package.json** тАФ all `@patternfly/*` packages to v6
- [ ] **Run main codemods** тАФ `npx @patternfly/pf-codemods@latest <src> --v6 --fix`
- [ ] **Run class-name-updater** тАФ `npx @patternfly/class-name-updater <src> --v6 --fix`
- [ ] **Run tokens-update** тАФ via pf-codemods `--only tokens-update`
- [ ] **Run css-vars-updater** тАФ for .css/.scss/.md files
- [ ] **Run data-codemods-cleanup** тАФ `--only data-codemods-cleanup --fix`
- [ ] **Install Victory** тАФ if using charts: `npm install victory`
- [ ] **Remove all CSS overrides** тАФ temporarily; re-add only necessary ones with new token names
- [ ] **Search for hot pink `--pf-t--temp--dev--tbd`** тАФ replace with appropriate PF6 tokens
- [ ] **Update breakpoint logic** тАФ any hardcoded pixel values тЖТ rem
- [ ] **Review EmptyState usage** тАФ significant refactor may need manual work
- [ ] **Review Masthead structure** тАФ wrap MastheadToggle/MastheadBrand in MastheadMain
- [ ] **Update DrawerHead usage** тАФ DrawerPanelBody no longer internal
- [ ] **Check `appendTo` on Dropdown/Select** тАФ default changed to `document.body`
- [ ] **Update test snapshots** тАФ regenerate all snapshots
- [ ] **Fix button tests** тАФ aria-disabled and byText issues
- [ ] **Fix select tests** тАФ hidden option issue
- [ ] **Review LogViewer stylesheet imports** тАФ now in LogViewer package
- [ ] **Check for removed components** тАФ Application Launcher, Context Selector, old Dropdown, Options Menu, Page Header, old Select
- [ ] **Replace Chip with Label** if not done by codemods
- [ ] **Replace Tile with Card** if not done by codemods
- [ ] **Update Text/TextContent/TextList тЖТ Content**
- [ ] **Verify OUIA component types** тАФ now `PF6/ComponentName`

