## Quick Reference: Recommended Upgrade Order

1. Create a feature branch
2. Update all `@patternfly/*` dependencies to v6
3. Install Victory peer dependency if using charts
4. Run `npx @patternfly/pf-codemods@latest <src> --v6` (dry run тАФ review)
5. Run `npx @patternfly/pf-codemods@latest <src> --v6 --fix` (auto-fix)
6. Run again to catch remaining issues; repeat until clean
7. Run `--only data-codemods-cleanup --fix`
8. Run class-name-updater with `--v6 --fix`
9. Run css-vars-updater for non-React files
10. Remove CSS overrides; re-add with new tokens where needed
11. Search for `--pf-t--temp--dev--tbd` and replace manually
12. Update breakpoint logic (px тЖТ rem)
13. Build and fix compile errors
14. Update/regenerate test snapshots
15. Fix test failures (button, select specifics)
16. Visual QA тАФ check for hot pink markers
17. Get help: [PatternFly Slack](https://join.slack.com/t/patternfly/shared_invite/zt-1npmqswgk-bF2R1E2rglV8jz5DNTezMQ) or [GitHub Discussions](https://github.com/orgs/patternfly/discussions)



