    <div class="score-card winner">
      <div class="name">semver/goose/053126-1221</div>
      <div class="score">79</div>
      <div class="label">/ 100 points</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="verdict-reasons">
    <strong>Key reasons:</strong>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Modal migration:</strong> Goose migrated ~30 modals from deprecated тЖТ new PF6 Modal API (correct direction). Codemods moved 1 modal <em>backwards</em> to deprecated.</li>
      <li><strong>Migration completeness:</strong> Goose addressed 144 files across modals, EmptyState, CSS cleanup, tests, DescriptionList, and dependency alignment. Codemods touched only 10 files.</li>
      <li><strong>No new bugs:</strong> Goose introduced zero new <code>icon={t('text')}</code> bugs. Codemods introduced 5 new instances of this incorrect pattern.</li>
      <li><strong>PF5 remnants removed:</strong> Goose eliminated all <code>pf-v5</code> references in source (0 remaining). Codemods left 4.</li>
      <li><strong>Tests updated:</strong> Goose fixed 13 test spec files for PF6 component behavior changes. Codemods updated none.</li>
      <li><strong>Scope concern:</strong> Goose loses points for React 17тЖТ18 upgrade and other non-PF dependency changes, but the core PF6 migration work is substantially superior.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>

